reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars good quality tempered glass
reviews.reviewText: It comes with cleaning pads to help install. It fits well and easy to apply. I initially did not place it well aligned on the phone screen, I was able to pry it off and reapplied a 2nd time successfully. It adhered without any bubble.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BEST iPhone screen protector
reviews.reviewText: I get screen protector all the time, I have 12 apple products in my house and this is the best by far. It’s very good quality at a cheap price, there is absolutely no air bubbles. Doesn’t seem like this type could even get air bubbles. Definitely recommend this brand!!!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Hated looking at the cracks in my screensaver for so long. Finally decided to replace. The fact that this was a 3 pack for $4 was such a great value. I agree that the wet & dry wipes are super small but, not a problem. My screen went on so smooth, no bubbles at all. Super satisfied.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to use
reviews.reviewText: The screen protectors are exactly as described and easy to use. When installing it I accidentally got a hair on the sticky part and it was super easy to remove and did not completely ruin the screen protector, as can occur with some of the other brands. Since then, I’ve dropped my phone a couple for times and have no damage to my phone or the screen protector. These are definitely going to be my go-to! :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Easy to install. Wipes to clean and placement stickers to help align glass.Take a cloth and push downward once the glass has latched on to screen and has set (appx 10-15 secs)Seems to be good quality and durable material to me. No bubbles!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So Far - So Good
reviews.reviewText: My iPhone screen broke because my actual phone case broke & didn’t realize it. Someone told me to grab a cover to hold the screen into place until I got it fixed. I will say if you put it on correctly & don’t touch the sticky side AT ALL it works great! You get 3 of them. And the price is so cheap! It’s not real thick but I didn’t care because my reason for purchasing was to hold it together so it wouldn’t get worse. So it worked for me. If you’re looking for a screen to protect your phone from cracking you might want a thicker one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My fell off my chair, only 2 feet from the ground and my screen cracked. I had this protector on my screen so I figured it’d be fine when once I took the protector off, the crack went right through it and my screen is cracked bad. Like I said, it fell off a normal chair, not aggressively, and it couldn’t even protect from that. DO NOT BUY THIS PIECE OF CRAP. You will just be paying way more to fix your actual screen later!!

reviews.reviewText: No scratches, Perfect fit, Crystal Clear screen.It’s holding up very nicely! Do recommend!
